System requirements
===================

   Total Chaos AGA requires a 68020 processor or better and OS 3.0 or
higher, and the AGA screen modes.

   Total Chaos requires 2 megs of chipram and 16 megs of fastram.

   It will only actually use about 1 meg of chipram and 11 megs of
fastram so you can still multitask.


