How to win
==========

   You have to:

   @{b}*@{ub} Kill all enemy wizards,

   @{b}*@{ub} kill or block all enemy generators,

   @{b}*@{ub} kill all enemy creatures that are still roaming around.

   A generator needs an empty space on which to generate creatures
onto. So if you can block all the spaces surrounding a generator, then
it cannot generate anything.  Corpses don't block a generator.
Generators are quite happy to generate monsters on top of dead corpses.
It gives them something to snack on. ;)


@EndNode

